The chorus girls’ routine from Death at the Cabaret
👯‍♀️
SO MUCH went into this dance. @callielangford is a brilliant choreographer who wrangled a big group of dancers and coaxed the best performances out of each of us. The counts matter and character counts. It was a lot of work. But there’s nothing like nailing a sequence with a group of dancers. Also… how fun that my character got to be an absolute menace.

Hey. You look good today.

Belated Porto appreciation post!
My first pole retreat was incredible - highly recommend @indipoleretreats ! I learned so much from @indipoledances @jazzykpole and @wesmarx at the workshops, met dancers from around the world, and got to experience so much of a beautiful city. And of course, the joy was multiplied by sharing the adventure with my SoFly babes @pole_gremlin @jwillrockyou @flora_june_ @veronikalynndance
